      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   v-key                  .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Modulo di Expand su righe ordine            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Preparazione valori per la chiamata     *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      v-cnt                to   w-mpn                  .
           move      w-mpn-dat-doc        to   w-esp-rig-ofr-dat      .
           move      w-mpn-num-doc        to   w-esp-rig-ofr-num      .
           move      w-mpn-tmo-orf        to   w-esp-rig-ofr-tmo      .
           move      w-mpn-num-prt        to   w-esp-rig-ofr-prt      .
           move      spaces               to   w-esp-rig-ofr-pro      .
