      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           perform   esp-rig-ofr-esp-000  thru esp-rig-ofr-esp-999    .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Uscita                                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     qry-trt-fun-999.
       qry-trt-fun-700.
      *              *=================================================*
      *              * Se function-key F4: espansione elemento per     *
      *              *                     documenti correlati         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Normalizzazione function key                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   v-key                  .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Modulo di Expand su documenti correlati     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Preparazione valori per la chiamata     *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      v-cnt                to   w-mpn                  .
           move      w-mpn-dat-doc        to   w-esp-ida-oft-dat      .
           move      w-mpn-num-doc        to   w-esp-ida-oft-num      .
           move      w-mpn-tmo-orf        to   w-esp-ida-oft-tmo      .
           move      w-mpn-num-prt        to   w-esp-ida-oft-prt      .
